<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="139" type="type species">
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="139">Type species.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="139">
<taxonomicName class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Helix (Chloritis) pseudomiara" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="2" pageNumber="139" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="pseudomiara" subGenus="Chloritis">Helix (Chloritis) pseudomiara</taxonomicName>
Bavay &amp; Dautzenberg, 1909 by monotypy.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="139">
The anatomically-examined specimen (i.e., on which the genus is based) was in fact 
<taxonomicName class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Helix condoriana" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="2" pageNumber="139" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="condoriana">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="139">Helix condoriana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Under the provisions of Article 70.3 ICZN, we herewith replace the original type species 
<taxonomicName class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Helix (Chloritis) pseudomiara" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="2" pageNumber="139" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="pseudomiara" subGenus="Chloritis">Helix (Chloritis) pseudomiara</taxonomicName>
Bavay &amp; Dautzenberg, 1909 with 
<taxonomicName class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Helix condoriana" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="2" pageNumber="139" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="condoriana">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="139">Helix condoriana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Crosse &amp; Fischer, 1863 as the type species of 
<taxonomicName class="Gastropoda" family="Camaenidae" genus="Bellatrachia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bellatrachia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="2" pageNumber="139" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="139">Bellatrachia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Schileyko, 2018 to serve the stability of nomenclature.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="139" type="included species">
